<div class="container">
	<div class="row about header">
		<h3>
			About TraitDB 
		</h3>
		<p>
			TraitDB is a web application built to facilitate storage and searching of trait data. Data are loaded from CSV files and organized into projects. Each project has a template for datasets, and TraitDB performs extensive validation when CSV files are uploaded. 
		<p>
	</div>
	<div class="row about source-code">
		<h3>
			Source Code 
		</h3>
		<p>
			TraitDB is open source software. Source code is available on <a href="https://github.com/NESCent/TraitDB"> GitHub </a> under an <a href="https://github.com/NESCent/TraitDB/raw/master/LICENSE.txt"> MIT License </a> 
		</p>
		<p>
			TraitDB uses <a href="http://travis-ci.org"> Travis CI </a> for continuous integration. Automated tests are run with each commit to the repository, build status is reported at <a href="https://travis-ci.org/NESCent/TraitDB">travis-ci.org/NESCent/TraitDB</a>. 
		</p>
		<p>
			Please report issues using the <a href="https://github.com/NESCent/TraitDB/issues"> GitHub Issue Tracker</a>. 
	</div>
